usdSubscriberAgentV1.name: usdSubscriberAgentV1
usdSubscriberAgentV1.productrelease:
Version 1 of the Subscriber component of the Unisphere Routing Switch
        SNMP agent.  This version of the Subscriber component was supported in
        the Unisphere RX 3.x system releases.
usdSubscriberAgentV1.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for subscriber capabilities in the Unisphere Routing Switch. These capabilities became obsolete when local authentication support was added.

usdSubscriberAgentV2.name: usdSubscriberAgentV2
usdSubscriberAgentV2.productrelease:
Version 2 of the Subscriber component of the Unisphere Routing Switch
        SNMP agent.  This version of the Subscriber component is supported in
        the Unisphere RX 4.0 and subsequent system releases.
usdSubscriberAgentV2.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for subscriber capabilities in the Unisphere Routing Switch.
